<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7234937>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Ochraethes nigroapicalis sp. nov. A–D. Holotype, ♂ (EMEC). A. Habitus, dorsal. B. Habitus, ventral. C. Habitus, lateral. D. Frons. E. Paratype, ♂ (CNIN), ventral view of male genitalia. F. Paratype, ♀ (EMEC), habitus, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7234937/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7234949>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Species delimitation in Ochraethes Chevrolat, 1860. Maximum likelihood tree inferred from COI in IQ TREE. The molecular operational taxonomic units (MOTU) are separated by colour bars. Abbreviations: ABGD = ast recursive analyses; bPTP = both Maximum likelihood and Bayesian analyses; GMYC = coalescence and yule analyses; MORP = morphology." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7234949/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

